episodes.title: Episode 13: JMAMT's New Groove
episodes.description: In this episode of Just Me and My Trauma, Kelsey and Jessi cover cults and brainwashing trauma!  We are trying a new format where we bounce back and forth off each other. Let us know if you like it!  Gloombreakers to "break up the gloom" include entries from r/ AmiTheDevil, r/AITA, r/creepyencounters, r/pettyrevenge, and r/TIFU on Reddit.   If you want to send in your own story or Gloombreaker, you can email Jessi and Kelsey: justtraumapodcast@gmail.com   If you want to see the pictures related to the stories, follow us on Instagram: justmeandmytrauma_pod  If you want to support us like the nice person you are, feel free to buy us a coffee:  ⁠www.buymeacoffee.com/justtraumapodcast⁠⁠  Become a Patronie!!  https://www.patreon.com/JustMeAndMyTraumaPodcast⁠    Sources:  https://science.howstuffworks.com/life/inside-the-mind/human-brain/brainwashing.htm  https://www.wikihow.com/Start-a-Cult  https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8234595/   https://listverse.com/2021/01/27/top-10-evil-cults-you-may-not-have-heard-of/
